

how to run:

    run run_game.py in the console

how to play:
    use the arrow keys to move the 'slime monster'


problems:
No sound on windows?

    'AVbin is required to decode compressed media')
    pyglet.media.riff.WAVEFormatException: AVbin is required to decode compressed media

    -> download it from http://code.google.com/p/avbin/downloads/list

    save the avbin.dll next to python.exe, not in windows/system32 as suggested in the readme
    